title: AI Agents
description: This course provides an in-depth look at AI agents, their design, application, and evaluation.
learningObjectives: Understand the fundamental concepts and theories of AI agents
Develop basic AI agents using Python
Evaluate and adjust AI agents performance

finalProjectDetails.overview: For the final project, students will design, implement, and evaluate an AI agent.
finalProjectDetails.submissionInstructions: Submit all project requirements in a single zipped folder
